YOU HAVE SUCCESSFULLY OPTED OUT!
We’re sorry to see you go, but Lotame has placed an opt-out cookie in your browser.
This cookie will prevent Lotame from tailoring the ads you see based on the anonymous information Lotame collects, as described further in
Lotame’s privacy policy
. This opt-out applies only to this browser and this computer, and you must repeat the process if you switch to a different browser or computer. Lotame is a member of the Network Advertising Initiative (NAI). If you would like to opt-out of Lotame together with other NAI members using the NAI’s opt-out tool, you can do so by
clicking here
Unfortunately, we were unable to confirm an opt-out cookie was set. Your browser must be set to accept cookies in order for the Lotame opt-out tool to work.
Lotame helps websites tailor the ads you see by using cookies (
https://www.networkadvertising.org/understanding-online-advertising/how-does-it-work
). Since your browser blocks access to these cookies, we do not coordinate ad placement across websites.
If you still wanted to explicitly opt-out, you can change your browser settings to accept cookies and retry our opt-out tool. Afterwards, you can return your browser to its previous cookie handling behavior. This opt-out would apply only to this browser and this computer. You must repeat the process if you clear your cookie history or change either your browser or computer.
Please note, websites can still place first-party cookies to record browsing activity while you are browsing their sites.
You can click on the Opt-Out button above to opt-out of having the Lotame Platform used by our Business Customers and Data Partners to collect any Personal Data from this browser and to stop use of the Lotame Cookie ID for interest-based advertising, content personalization, or any other purpose.
When you click on the Opt-Out button, an opt-out cookie (from crwdcntrl.com) will be stored in your browser so that our Platform will know the choice you have made when it sees the opt-out cookie, and your choice will apply to all our Business Customers and Data Partners. Additionally, the Lotame Cookie ID will be deleted from our Platform.
You can also use the third-party tools listed below:
In the United States, you can use the Digital Advertising Alliance’s
WebChoices Tool
or the Network Advertising Initiative’s (NAI)
